{"tid":2215170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧控中國施壓美國地方官員 不得與台灣往來","createTime":"2020-09-23T20:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T13:24:39.000Z","uid":337052,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ab01e5faf51a15ade82d644979ccf72468e549","tid":2215170,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T20:45:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">蓬佩奧控中國施壓美國地方官員 不得與台灣往來</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/09/24 02:58<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者徐薇婷華盛頓23日專電）<span class=\"red\">美國國務卿蓬佩奧今天赴威斯康辛州參議會發表演說，指控中國施壓美國州政府不得承認或與台灣往來。蓬佩奧呼籲地方政府應無視中共威脅，鼓勵市長及企業人士與世界各地來往。<br />\n</span><br />\n美國大選進入最後40天衝刺，國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）今天造訪6大關鍵搖擺州之一的威斯康辛州，並於州參議會針對中國挑戰發表演說。根據駐美代表處，駐芝加哥台北經濟文化辦事處處長黃鈞耀也出席同場活動。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧於演說中指出，今年8月，中共總書記習近平告訴一群政府經濟與社會學家，北京必須與所有願意與中國合作的國家、區域與企業發展合作，包含美國各州及地區。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧表示：「容我為大家翻譯，習近平知道美國聯邦政府起身抵抗中共與其惡意影響力&hellip;他認為地方領袖是薄弱環節。對習近平來說，當他使用『合作』與『開放』這兩個字眼，指的是他希望創造有利中共的安排。」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">蓬佩奧說，中共將目標鎖定州層級官員與地方利益，近來力道越來越大，行動重點大多圍繞在施壓州政府，不得承認台灣或與台灣有貿易及其他往來。</span><br />\n<br />\n不只如此，蓬佩奧指出，中共影響力與間諜行動觸角還伸向縣市層級。他說，本週稍早，一位紐約市員警被控非法擔任中國政府的間諜，向中國回報旅美藏族社群的行動。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧接著向全美州議員喊話：「若有中國外交人員與你接洽，出發點可能不是合作或友誼；若疫情旅遊限制解除後，有人邀請你去中國，你該問問旅費是由誰支付，以及該人士是否直接或間接與中共有關聯。」<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧指出，州議會其實有很多可做，例如通過法律增進州與聯邦政府間合作，保護智慧財產權、過濾投資基金，及對抗滲透行動等；州議會也能無視中共威脅，鼓勵市長與企業人士與世界各地更廣泛往來，及確保在美國就學、支持民主的中國、香港及台灣學生，不會被騷擾。<br />\n<br />\n他強調：「為了美國人民及歷史上最偉大民主國家的未來，讓我們一起共同合作。」（編輯：楊昭彥）1090924<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202009240009.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202009240009.aspx&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=9b536494\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202009240009.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"48848b09cb16258701816a37fc2cf6d1585b4188","tid":2215170,"uid":337052,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T20:54:04.000Z","msg":"US Secretary of State Mike Pompeo warns US politicians to be alert to Chinese 'influence and espionage'<br />\nPompeo said the State Department was reviewing the activities of the US-China Friendship Association and the China Council for the Promotion of Peaceful Reunificarution.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zeenews.india.com/world/us-secretary-of-state-mike-pompeo-warns-us-politicians-to-be-alert-to-chinese-influence-and-espionage-2311940.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzeenews.india.com%2Fworld%2Fus-secretary-of-state-mike-pompeo-warns-us-politicians-to-be-alert-to-chinese-influence-and-espionage-2311940.html&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=0988c707\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zeenews.india.com/world/us-secretary-of-state-mike-pompeo-warns-us-politicians-to-be-alert-to-chinese-influence-and-espionage-2311940.html</a><br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧警告美國官員不要接觸中共官員"},{"pid":"ee0c02c867b370237f549f3a167a8c49146652d9","tid":2215170,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T20:57:23.000Z","msg":"Secretary of State Mike Pompeo warns against Chinese influence in speech to state lawmakers<br />\nRILEY VETTERKIND Sep 23, 2020 Updated 36 min ago  0<br />\n<a href=\"https://journaltimes.com/news/state-and-regional/govt-and-politics/secretary-of-state-mike-pompeo-warns-against-chinese-influence-in-speech-to-state-lawmakers/article_5b3286c0-7a9b-5d0c-8f35-b5e4694286f4.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjournaltimes.com%2Fnews%2Fstate-and-regional%2Fgovt-and-politics%2Fsecretary-of-state-mike-pompeo-warns-against-chinese-influence-in-speech-to-state-lawmakers%2Farticle_5b3286c0-7a9b-5d0c-8f35-b5e4694286f4.html&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=bf52d3e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://journaltimes.com/news/state-and-regional/govt-and-politics/secretary-of-state-mike-pompeo-warns-against-chinese-influence-in-speech-to-state-lawmakers/article_5b3286c0-7a9b-5